No. 09-861. Citizens for Police Accountability Political Committee, Petitioner v. Kurt S. Browning, Florida Secretary of State, et al. 559 U.S. 1086, 130 S. Ct. 2141,

176 L. Ed. 2d 756,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3204. April 19, 2010.

Motion of Marion B. Brechner First Amendment Project, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.

Same case below, 572 F.3d 1213.
